2005-05-10  appel

	* [r1116] trunk/testsuite/Makefile.am, trunk/testsuite/finite_systems_1d/helium.test,
	  trunk/testsuite/finite_systems_3d/sodium.test, trunk/testsuite/run_regression.pl:
