2004-01-27  micael

	* [r646] trunk/src/eigen_plan.F90, trunk/src/f.F90, trunk/src/mf_inc.F90,
	  trunk/src/states.F90, trunk/src/states_inc.F90, trunk/src/td_exp.F90, trunk/src/xc.F90,
	  trunk/src/xc_GGA.F90:
	  *) Started hiding BLAS calls.

