2003-06-17  rozzi

	* [r469] trunk/src/ps.F90:
	  I need the logrid to integrate the local pseudo part, but I am not able to get it as a
	  pointer, so I have awfully copied the part of the structure I need. I hope it will be more
	  elegant in future.
