2002-05-04  acastro

	* [r147] trunk/share/PP/HGH, trunk/share/PP/HGH/C.hgh, trunk/share/PP/HGH/H.hgh,
	  trunk/share/PP/HGH/He.hgh, trunk/share/PP/HGH/Na.hgh, trunk/share/PP/HGH/Ti.hgh,
